      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\" alt\u003d\"\" /\u003e\r\n  \u003ch3\u003eDocument Guidelines Compliance Check\u003c/h3\u003e\r\n  \u003c/div\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eGuidelines Compliance Check\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n  \u003cp\u003e\r\n  A compliance check is a process used by organizations to ensure that they are adhering to internal policies, legal regulations, and industry standards.\r\n  \u003c/p\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n    \u003cul\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Upload Marketing Documents for a raw compliance check based on the below metrics\u003c/li\u003e\r\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Or, upload a Guidelines document and a sample document to run a comparitive compliance check\u003c/li\u003e\r\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ch4\u003eWhat We Check:\u003c/h4\u003e\r\n  \u003cul\u003e\r\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Identify all relevant laws, regulations, standards, and internal policies that apply to the organization or specific processes within it. This aligns to regular reviewing and monitoring of practices, processes, and systems to ensure they comply with the identified requirements.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n  \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e Identify and mitigate compliance risks to prevent violations that could result in legal penalties, financial loss, or reputational damage. This educates employees and stakeholders about compliance requirements and fosters a culture of compliance within the organization.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n  \u003c/ul\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n\r\n  \u003csection\u003e\r\n  \u003ctable style\u003d\"width: 99.5%; border-collapse: collapse; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cthead\u003e\r\n  \u003ctr style\u003d\"background-color: #787575; color: white; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003e\r\n  \u003cth scope\u003d\"col\" style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; text-align: left; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eCheck Point\u003c/th\u003e\r\n  \u003cth scope\u003d\"col\" style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; text-align: left; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eWhat We Verify\u003c/th\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n  \u003c/thead\u003e\r\n  \u003ctbody class\u003d\"small\"\u003e\r\n  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eIdentification\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eVerify if the marketing communication includes a clear statement identifying it as such, including the terms \u0027marketing communication\u0027, and a disclaimer referring to the relevant prospectus or KIID/KID for further information.\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eRisk and Reward Disclosure\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eCheck if information on risks and rewards is given with equal prominence in terms of placement, font size, and style, and if the description of risks is integrated within the main body of the text rather than hidden in footnotes.\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eFair, Clear, and Not Misleading Information\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eAssess if the language used in the communication is clear and free of excessive technical jargon, and if the communication avoids making misleading statements or omissions that could mislead investors.\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eConsistency with Legal Documents\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eEnsure the details provided in the marketing communication are consistent with the prospectus, KIID/KID, and other regulatory documents of the fund, and that any figures or claims about performance, costs, or returns match those in the legal documents.\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eInvestment Features Description\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eVerify if the content describes the investment policy accurately and clearly, includes a clear explanation of the types of assets into which the fund may invest, and explains how leverage affects potential losses or returns if mentioned.\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctr\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003ePresentation Quality\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003ctd style\u003d\"font-size: 16px; padding: 8px; border: 2px solid #ccc;\"\u003eCheck if the content is presented in a readable format, with appropriate font size and style, if audio/visual elements are clear and easily understandable, if all statements are supported by objective, verifiable sources, and if the communication avoids implying endorsement or approval by national authorities.\u003c/td\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tr\u003e\r\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\r\n  \u003c/table\u003e\r\n  \u003c/section\u003e\r\n  \r\n \u003c/div\u003e",
